**Privacy Policy for Funky Bot**

**Last Updated: [Date]**

### 1. Introduction

Funky is a Discord music bot designed to enhance server engagement by providing high-quality music playback. This Privacy Policy explains how Funky handles user data within Discord.

### 2. Data We Collect

Funky only processes the following data:

- **Message Content:** Required to detect and respond to prefix-based music commands (e.g., `+play`, `+pause`, `+skip`).
- **User & Server Information:** Discord user IDs, server IDs, and channel IDs for executing bot commands.

### 3. How We Use Data

We use the collected data to:

- Process and execute music commands.
- Improve bot functionality and ensure a seamless user experience.

### 4. Data Storage & Security

- Funky **does not** store or retain message content outside of Discord.
- We **do not** share, sell, or distribute any user data to third parties.
- All data is processed in real-time and discarded immediately after use.

### 5. User Control & Opt-Out

- Since Funky only processes data in real-time, users do not need to opt-out as no data is stored.
- If a server owner wishes to disable Funky, they can remove the bot from their server at any time.

### 6. Contact Information

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at: 

Gmail : [rexx001r@gmail.com](mailto\:rexx001r@gmail.com) 

DISCORD SERVER : https\://discord.gg/W5CqWNfYKh

### 7. Changes to This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Users will be notified of significant changes through the bot's official support channels.
